oai_dc:dc.dc:title: DIARYLHEPTANOIDS FROM GARUGA-PINNATA
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: VENKATRAMAN, G
MISHRA, AK
THOMBARE, PS
SABATA, BK
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: biphenyl ether
garuga-pinnata
burseraceae
stem bark
macrocyclic biphenyl and biphenyl ethers
diarylheptanoids
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The structures of three new diarylheptanoids of the biphenyl ether and biphenyl type, garuganins IV-VI, isolated from the petrol and chloroform extract of stem bark of Garuga pinnata, were established by spectroscopic methods (UV, IR, H-1 NMR, C-13 NMR) and chemical reactions.
